data.description: SAY HELLO TO YOUR NEW HOME FOR THE NEW YEAR! Introducing this affordable home priced below $200k, located at 515 Patton Drive! This charming raised ranch offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. With 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, including an attached half bath in the primary bedroom, this home is ideal for your family's needs. The spacious, finished walkout basement provides all the space for your lifestyle. Enjoy the ease of daily life with a move-in ready home. The 1-car garage and fenced backyard offer security and privacy, all while backing up to tranquil woods. Nestled on a peaceful cul de sac, this home is not just a house; it's your sanctuary. Don't miss the chance to make it yours!
